nginx is a open source tool which can be a web server,reverse proxy server ,laod balancer ,content cache ,API gateway ,Kubernetes ingress controller ,web application firewall.

Nginx plus architecture      ---master process. (It reads as well as evaluates configuration and maintains worker processes)
                             ---Child processes (It actually does the processing of the requests)
                             ---Non-blocking
                             ---Nginx reload 

Configuration file locations  ---- /etc/nginx/nginx.conf
                              ---- /etc/nginx/conf.d/default.conf
    
    
Nginx commands :  nginx -v
                  nginx -t (check configuraton)
                  nginx -T (view configuration)
                  nginx -s reload (reload configuration)
